---
title: Carb Smart Almond Chicken with Parmesan, Green Veggies and Lemony Mayo
description: This is not your nonna's Parmesan chicken! Inspired by a restaurant classic, tender chicken is topped with a garlicky Parmesan crust! We've swapped breadcrumbs out for almonds to keep those carbs low. A tumble of garlicky green veggies is always wholesome!

